---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="关于｜推知 Inferred"
  description="Inferred 是一个原创互动推理项目。这里的每一篇内容都是一份等待被阅读、质疑和推断的案卷。"
  path="/about"
>
  <article class="container container--reading about">
    <header class="about__header">
      <p class="eyebrow">About · 关于</p>
      <h1>
        <span class="i18n-zh">关于 推知 Inferred</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">About Inferred</span>
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose about__body">
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">Inferred 是一个原创互动推理项目。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">Inferred is an original interactive mystery project.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">起始的动因因为女儿糖糖，她是一个悬疑爱好者。高一的年纪已经读了很多侦探小说。我希望通过这个项目给她学习之外的时间多点思考。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">It started because of my daughter Tangtang, a mystery enthusiast who had already read many detective novels by the time she entered high school. I wanted this project to give her something to think about beyond her studies.</span>
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">这里的每一篇内容都不是单纯的故事，而是一份等待被阅读、质疑和推断的案卷。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">Every piece here is not merely a story, but a case file waiting to be read, questioned, and reasoned through.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">你会看到人物、证词、物证、时间线和看似无关的细节。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">You'll encounter characters, testimonies, physical evidence, timelines, and details that seem unrelated.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">其中一部分是真的。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">Some of it is true.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">一部分是误导。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">Some of it is a misdirection.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">还有一部分，只有在你重新阅读时才会显露意义。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">And some only reveals its meaning when you read it again.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">如果引起了糖糖，以及你的思考，这本身就具备了它存在的意义。</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">If it sparks Tangtang's thinking — and yours — that's reason enough for it to exist.</span>
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p>
        <span class="i18n-zh">如果你有任何想法、建议，或者只是想聊聊某个案子，欢迎来信：</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">If you have any thoughts, suggestions, or just want to talk through a case, write to us:</span>
      </p>
      <p><a href="mailto:hztbc001@gmail.com">hztbc001@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: var(--space-16);
  }
  .about__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  .about__body p {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
</style>
